cs.CV, cs.TR, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper extensively uses computer vision techniques for vehicle detection, tracking and speed calculation. 
2. cs.TR (Transportation) - The paper deals with the problem of vehicle speed monitoring and management on highways, which falls under the domain of transportation. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics) - The proposed system can be considered as a robotic system that monitors and manages the traffic on highways. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper uses an HD camera for recording video frames, which falls under the domain of multimedia. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed system uses pattern recognition and mathematical techniques for vehicle detection, tracking and speed calculation, which can be considered as AI techniques.
